Dear WebAuth User,

We=E2=80=99re introducing a new way to experience WebAuth =E2=80=94 now ava=
ilable on desktop.

With the launch of WebAuth Desktop, you can manage your assets in a more fo=
cused, secure environment designed for clarity and control. Instead of rely=
ing on browser extensions or switching between tools, everything now lives =
in one dedicated space built for serious crypto activity.

WebAuth Desktop brings the full power of the XPR ecosystem directly to your=
 computer. You can stake XPR, connect to MetalX for decentralized trading, =
and manage all your assets in one place with a clear view of your portfolio=
 and activity. Every transaction is signed locally on your device, giving y=
ou an added layer of security and confidence when moving or managing funds

Security remains at the core of WebAuth. Your private keys stay encrypted o=
n your device, protected by biometric authentication, and never leave your =
control. You can also sync across devices, allowing you to move seamlessly =
between mobile and desktop while maintaining full ownership of your assets

This is more than just a new interface. It=E2=80=99s a cleaner way to inter=
act with your crypto. From username-based transfers to zero network fees wi=
thin the XPR Network, WebAuth Desktop removes friction and makes everyday a=
ctions feel simple and reliable


You can explore the desktop experience here: https://www.webauthdesktop.co/


If you already use WebAuth, getting started is simple. Install the app, con=
nect your existing account, and continue where you left off with a more pow=
erful setup.

If you have any questions or need help getting started, our support team is=
 available through the chat widget on the download page.

